net.sf.mmm.util.property.api.lang

Interface ReadableIntegerBindingProperty<N extends Number>

  • Type Parameters:
    N - is the generic type of the internal numeric value representation.
    All Superinterfaces:
    AttributeReadName, AttributeReadValue<Number>, javafx.beans.binding.NumberExpression, javafx.beans.Observable, javafx.beans.value.ObservableNumberValue, javafx.beans.value.ObservableValue<Number>, PropertyPath<Number>, ReadableNumberProperty<N>, ReadableProperty<Number>, javafx.beans.property.ReadOnlyProperty<Number>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ReadableByteProperty, ReadableIntegerProperty, ReadableShortProperty, WritableByteProperty, WritableIntegerProperty, WritableShortProperty
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractContainerProperty.SizeProperty, ByteProperty, IntegerProperty, IntegerPropertyExpression, ShortProperty

    public interface ReadableIntegerBindingProperty<N extends Number>
extends ReadableNumberProperty<N>
    This is the interface for a ReadableNumberProperty with a value-type with Integer, Short, or Byte.
    Since:
    8.0.0
